WEBVTT

00:02.193 --> 00:06.256
Every day I watch the weatherman on TV.

00:07.246 --> 00:10.443
Knowing about the weather is important to me.

00:11.508 --> 00:14.374
I want to know if the wind will blow.

00:15.379 --> 00:17.847
I want to know if it will rain.

00:18.831 --> 00:21.545
I want to know if it will snow.

00:22.703 --> 00:24.623
How is the weather today?

00:25.647 --> 00:28.680
The weatherman says warm with showers.

00:29.616 --> 00:34.529
I will wear my raincoat. I will go fishing with Dad.

00:36.197 --> 00:38.007
How is the weather today?

00:39.019 --> 00:44.809
The weatherman says it will be stormy. I will play in the house.

00:45.897 --> 00:47.746
How is the weather today?

00:48.695 --> 00:51.105
The weatherman says it will be hot.

00:52.078 --> 00:53.804
I will go to the beach.

00:55.295 --> 00:57.225
How is the weather today?

00:58.161 --> 01:01.570
The weatherman says it will be cool and windy.

01:02.565 --> 01:06.631
I will wear my jacket. I will fly my kite.

01:07.847 --> 01:09.732
How is the weather today?

01:10.753 --> 01:14.249
The weatherman says it will be cold and icy.

01:15.293 --> 01:17.407
I will wear my hat and coat.

01:18.325 --> 01:20.107
How is the weather today?

01:21.068 --> 01:23.516
The weatherman says it will snow.

01:24.539 --> 01:26.283
I will make a snowman.

01:27.361 --> 01:29.914
The weather changes with the seasons.

01:30.881 --> 01:32.701
I like changing weather.

01:33.737 --> 01:35.751
I can wear different clothes.

01:36.745 --> 01:38.728
I can do different things.

